\f1\b0\fs46 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}1/2 cup sliced almonds\
{\listtext	\'95	}3 cups chocolate morsels, (about 1 1/2 (12-ounce) bags)\
{\listtext	\'95	}1/2 cup dried cranberries\
{\listtext	\'95	}1/2 {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/tangerine/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 tangerine}}, zested\
